   For referrals to treatment programs, please call 1-800-662-HELP

   Announcements:
     * For Treatment Practitioners - Dextromethorphan Alert: The use of
       dextromethorphan as part of the detox regimen from methadone
       maintenance HAS NOT BEEN STUDIED FOR EFFICACY AND IS NOT ENCOURAGED
       BASED ON EXISTING RESEARCH FINDINGS.

   Publications: Go to Publications Catalog
     * NIDA Clinical Toolbox, science-based materials for drug abuse
       treatment providers.
     * Principles of Drug Addiction Treatment: A Research-Based Guide. The
       guide outlines some of the essential components of treatment based
       on 30 years of scientific research.
     * Measuring and Improving Costs, Cost-Effectiveness, and Cost-Benefit
       for Substance Abuse Treatment Programs

